{"tid":1262281,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"罷睇CCTVB幫手轉台計劃","createTime":"2019-06-27T15:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T07:46:01.000Z","uid":26966,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d2c139fe34f3077629ad344ef5c36faa4fb72ed3","tid":1262281,"uid":26966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"有鑒於香港許多老一輩與中年經常被CCTVB 潛移默化式洗腦，本人建議各位巴絲除了要幫家中電視轉台外，更要在有電視的公眾地方要求轉台。<br />\n<br />\n例如在餐廳<br />\n盡量同成班朋友拜託侍應幫手轉台<br />\n<br />\n在醫院<br />\n同院友拜託護士幫手轉台<br />\n<br />\n務求源頭減廢，令CCTVB減少禍害。<br />\n<br />\n雖然很老人家已經被洗腦多年，根深蒂固，但最小我們可幫他們停止吸毒，甚至令他們唔知洗腦內容，再慢慢洗返他們腦。"},{"pid":"0d043774971debde1563b4db0505e0815df63ba1","tid":1262281,"uid":26966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc5d545415c46c918be0a19aff27b2b8c5a65468","tid":1262281,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:03:00.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\n有個方法教大家長期整now/有線新聞台係電視度<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cRRRqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cRRRqS</a>"},{"pid":"73cf95516cfd274a69e46ceeff52f6e286b576c5","tid":1262281,"uid":209225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc5d545415c46c918be0a19aff27b2b8c5a65468","tid":1262281,"uid":264780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:03:00.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\n有個方法教大家長期整now/有線新聞台係電視度<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cRRRqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cRRRqS</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:03:50.000Z","msg":"聽日就G20，聽晚煲底見！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1262072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1262072</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kUFa5HJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkUFa5HJ.png&h=e2aae1ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d915314371147be55e029b099bb52c3a7ceed73","tid":1